meta.description: Symplectic bases for orientable N12_1..N12_29 (genus 6). Basis given as integer 1-cochains on oriented edges of K12 (66 edges). J is in interleaved order (e1,f1,e2,f2,...). Electric coordinates can be taken as e1..e6 (indices 0,2,4,6,8,10) and magnetic as f1..f6 (indices 1,3,5,7,9,11).
